&gt;&gt; To‘g’ri.
Va biz: "Xavotir olmang, 

00:00:29.140 --> 00:00:30.200
bu qanday ishlashi haqida 

00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:31.720
keyinroq gaplashamiz", degan edik

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.290
