00:00:37.560 --> 00:00:39.510
Talabalar ham metoddan
shunday foydalanishgan.

00:00:39.510 --> 00:00:40.035
&gt;&gt; Yaxshi.
&gt;&gt; To‘g’rimi?

00:00:40.035 --> 00:00:41.845
