&gt;&gt; MainActivity.java 
faylining ichida,

00:00:56.506 --> 00:00:59.540
display metodi aniqlangan.

00:00:59.540 --> 00:01:02.956
Bu yerda esa, u chaqiriladi

00:01:02.956 --> 00:01:04.769
increment va decrement 
metodi ichida.

00:01:04.769 --> 00:01:08.640
Display metod buyruqlari sonni oladi 

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:10.550
va uni ekranda aks ettiradi.

00:01:10.550 --> 00:01:11.730
Bu yerdagi kabi.

00:01:11.730 --> 00:01:16.360
Metodni aniqlashning o‘rniga biz 
shunchaki uning buyruqlarini olishimiz

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:21.300
va ularni metod chaqirilgan joyga 
nusxalashimiz mumkin.

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:25.580
Bu yerda number o‘zgaruvchi bo‘lmaganligi 
uchun biz uni quantity bilan almashtiramiz.

00:01:25.580 --> 00:01:26.550
Agar bu amalni 
increment metodi uchun 

00:01:26.550 --> 00:01:30.940
ham bajarish kerak bo‘lsa
kodni nusxalaymiz va shu yerga joylaymiz. 

00:01:30.940 --> 00:01:33.740
Shunday qilib, 
kod avvalgidek ishlayapti, 

00:01:33.740 --> 00:01:35.950
ammo endi bizga 
display metodi kerak emas.

00:01:35.950 --> 00:01:40.060
Bunday amalning kamchiligi shundaki, 
ikki metodda ham 

00:01:40.060 --> 00:01:41.150
kodni takrorlash kerak.

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:46.170
Buning o‘rniga, agar biz display 
metodini aniqlasak va uni chaqirsak,

00:01:46.170 --> 00:01:49.500
ilovaning yaxshiroq ishlashi uchun 
qatorlari kamroq bo‘lgan kodni olamiz.

00:01:49.500 --> 00:01:51.670
Men sizga yana bir ajoyib 
narsani ko‘rsatmoqchiman.

00:01:51.670 --> 00:01:55.540
Metodni ko‘rganingizda, uni belgilab 
sichqonchaning o‘ng tugmasini bosishingiz mumkin.

00:01:55.540 --> 00:01:59.340
Keyin Go To - Declaration yoki agar 
sizda Mac bo‘lsa, Command + V ni bosing.

00:02:00.610 --> 00:02:04.100
Kod metod aniqlangan, 
yani define qilingan, joygacha tushadi.

00:02:04.100 --> 00:02:07.650
Buning foydaliligi shundaki, siz buyruqlarni

00:02:07.650 --> 00:02:09.490
metod ichida ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

00:02:09.490 --> 00:02:10.300
Boshqa metodlarda bu 

00:02:10.300 --> 00:02:14.480
Android framework kodining 
o‘zida declaration ni ochishi mumkin.

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:18.940
Bu TextView.java fayl 
Android jamoasi tomonidan yozilgan.

00:02:18.940 --> 00:02:22.200
Bu hammasi sehr kabi bo‘lib ko‘rinsada 

00:02:22.200 --> 00:02:26.150
barchasi aniqlanadigan kodni 
topishingiz mumkin ekanligini ko‘rsatadi.

00:02:26.150 --> 00:02:29.970
Kod siz yoki Android jamoasi tomonidan 
aniqlangan bo‘ladi.

00:02:29.970 --> 00:02:33.150
Metodning ta’rifi(defining ) va chaqiruvi(calling ) 
orasidagi farqni tushunishingizga yordam berish uchun

00:02:33.150 --> 00:02:35.930
MainActivity ni o‘zgartiramiz.

00:02:35.930 --> 00:02:38.960
Biz metod aniqlangan usulni, 
metodning nomini

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:42.585
display dan diaplayQuantity ga 
almashtirish yordamida o‘zgartirmoqchimiz.

00:02:42.585 --> 00:02:47.450
Keyinchalik, bu metodni chaqirish uchun biz 
yana biror narsani o‘zgartirishimiz kerakmi?

00:02:47.450 --> 00:02:51.710
Agar bu o‘zgartirishlardan so‘ng, 
ilovada xatolik bo‘lsa

00:02:51.710 --> 00:02:53.770
ilovani telefonda ishga tushirish 
uchun xatoni to‘g‘irlang.

00:02:53.770 --> 00:02:55.100
Yakunlaganingizdan so‘ng 
bu yerda belgilang.

